title: The Oasis Video That Never Happened
original_title: The Oasis Video That Never Happened
overview: Spike Jonze and his team visit the UK and interview members of the public, asking them to imagine an Oasis music video that they'll star in with the band. Oasis didn't like anyone's ideas and so the video was never made, but Spike still made his film.
